Definition: tending to cure or restore to health
Example: curative powers of herbal remedies; her gentle healing hand; remedial surgery; a sanative environment of mountains and fresh air; a therapeutic agent; therapeutic diets
Synonyms: verb, body, cure, healing, p, alterative, remedial, noun, artifact, remedy, sanative, therapeutic, tending, to, or, restore, health, powers, of, herbal, remedies, her, gentle, hand, surgery, a, environment, mountains, and, fresh, air, agent, diets
Category: adj.all
